graph TD
    A[Raw Text] --> B[Tokenizer / Vocabulary]
    B -->|Integer IDs| C[Embedding Layer]
    C -->|Dense Vectors| D[LSTM Cell]
    
    subgraph LSTM Time Steps
    D -->|Step 1: Word 1| E[Hidden State 1]
    E -->|Step 2: Word 2 + Hidden 1| F[Hidden State 2]
    F -->|Step N: Word N + Hidden N-1| G[Final Hidden State]
    end
    
    G --> H[Linear Classifier]
    H --> I[Prediction]
